title: Plz Help Me Figure This Out
body:
So for a long time now I have asked this question but could never find a answer... (What happens if five {{champion:53}}  Pull one champion at the same time? I'm talking all hands hit the target at the same time. I would really like an answer so plz commit back if you know or have any thoughts... 


          TheTomokiTower
